02:00.350 --> 02:01.180
Dont forget.

02:01.220 --> 02:03.180
As with the select statement.

02:03.350 --> 02:07.300
Any columns that you use in the WHERE clause should have an index.

02:07.470 --> 02:11.910
Otherwise they could take a long time to execute.

02:15.010 --> 02:17.570
One more thing about the update statement.

02:17.740 --> 02:24.460
If you don't include aware class every single row in the table will be updated.

02:24.460 --> 02:30.760
So unless you actually want to do this make sure you always include a WHERE clause to only update the

02:30.760 --> 02:32.960
